text: Mohamed Sayed Hamdi (11 December 1931 - 16 October 1992) was an Egyptian gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1952 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1931 births Category:1992 deaths Category:Egyptian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Egypt Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing
